esident%20came%20while%20addressing%20reporters%20on%20his%20return%20to%20the%20Maldives%20from%20a%20five-day%20state%20visit%20to%20China%20on%20Saturday%2C%20January%2014.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20the%20first%20major%20election%20into%20Muizzu%E2%80%99s%20presidency%2C%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20lost%20the%20capital%20city%20Mal%C3%A9%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.sun.mv%2F87039%5C%22%3Em%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.sun.mv%2F87039%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eayoral%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20elections%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20the%20opposition%2C%20Maldivian%20Democratic%20Party.%20This%20election%20was%20necessitated%20by%20Muizzu%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20as%20Mal%C3%A9%20mayor%20following%20his%20victory%20in%20last%20November%E2%80%99s%20presidential%20election.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20weekend%2C%20the%20Maldivian%20government%20had%20%E2%80%9Csuspended%E2%80%9D%20three%20deputy%20ministers%20for%20making%20disparaging%20remarks%20against%20the%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20after%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20Lakshadweep%20islands.%20Following%20the%20tweets%2C%20several%20Indian%20celebrities%20started%20to%20post%20together%20that%20they%20will%20boycott%20the%20Maldives%20as%20a%20tourist%20destination.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20government%20had%20summoned%20the%20Maldivian%20ambassador%20to%20South%20Block%20last%20Monday.%20On%20the%20same%2C%20the%20Indian%20envoy%20went%20to%20the%20Maldivian%20foreign%20ministry%20for%20what%20was%20later%20described%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpre-arranged%E2%80%9D%20meeting.%20It%20had%20seemed%20that%20the%20two%20sides%20were%20trying%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20temperature%20as%20neither%20side%20provided%20any%20further%20details.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%2C%20Muizzu%20on%20return%20to%20Maldives%20seemed%20to%20have%20jumped%20into%20the%20fray.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Licence%20to%20bully%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20in%20the%20backyard%20of%20any%20particular%20country.%20We%20are%20an%20independent%20and%20sovereign%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20answer%20to%20a%20question%20at%20a%20media%20conference%20at%20the%20Velana%20International%20Airport.%20He%20asserted%20that%20China%20respected%20Maldives%E2%80%99%20territorial%20integrity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Maldivian%20President%20stated%20that%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20is%20not%20the%20exclusive%20domain%20of%20any%20specific%20nation%20and%20noted%20that%20the%20Maldives%20holds%20a%20significant%20stake%20in%20the%20vast%20expanse%20of%20this%20ocean.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20though%20our%20islands%20are%20small%2C%20we%20are%20a%20huge%20country%20with%20a%20very%20large%20exclusive%20economic%20zone%20of%20nine%20lakh%20square%20kilometres.%20Maldives%20is%20one%20country%20that%20holds%20the%20largest%20proportion%20of%20this%20ocean.%20This%20ocean%20is%20not%20the%20property%20of%20a%20specific%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuizzu%20even%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20earlier%20President%20Mohamed%20Solih%20for%20having%20a%20close%20relation%20with%20India%2C%20but%20without%20mentioning%20New%20Delhi%20directly.%20He%20said%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Maldivian%20media%2C%20that%20Solih%20had%20to%20take%20permission%20from%20a%20foreign%20government%20%E2%80%9Cto%20get%20up%20from%20one%20chair%20and%20sit%20on%20another%20chair%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuizzu%20had%20won%20the%20presidential%20elections%20and%20stopped%20Solih%E2%80%99s%20re-election%20bid%20by%20campaigning%20on%20a%20platform%20with%20the%20slogan%20of%20%E2%80%98India%20Out%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmaldives-president-asks-india-to-withdraw-its-troops%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20second%20day%20of%20his%20presidency%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Muizzu%20had%20called%20on%20India%20to%20remove%20Indian%20security%20personnel%20stationed%20in%20Maldives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20might%20be%20a%20small%20country%2C%20but%20that%20does%20not%20give%20you%20the%20licence%20to%20bully%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrade%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETill%20now%2C%20all%20democratically-elected%20Maldivian%20Presidents%20had%20chosen%20India%20as%20their%20first%20foreign%20trip.%20Muizzu%20chose%20to%20go%20to%20Turkey%20and%20then%20UAE%20last%20year%2C%20following%20which%20he%20travelled%20to%20China%20for%20his%20first%20state%20visit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Maldivian%20President%20pledged%20to%20diminish%20Maldives%E2%80%99%20reliance%20on%20India%20across%20multiple%20sectors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMaldives%20primarily%20relies%20on%20India%20as%20its%20main%20supplier%20of%20essential%20commodities%2C%20with%20New%20Delhi%20providing%20a%20special%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcontent.dgft.gov.in%2FWebsite%2Fdgftprod%2Fae06ad43-ecbd-40b1-afff-53a2f8649e30%2FNoti%252014%2520Eng.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eannual%20quota%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20items%20such%20as%20eggs%2C%20potatoes%2C%20sugar%2C%20dal%2C%20rice%2C%20wheat%20flour%2C%20stone%20aggregates%2C%20and%20river%20sand%2C%20exempt%20from%20restrictions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.sun.mv%2F87038%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20media%20reports%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Muizzu%20said%20that%20the%20government%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20hopefully%20stop%20bringing%20low-quality%20medicine%20and%20opt%20to%20bring%20medicine%20directly%20from%20the%20orig