posed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20consider%20this%20to%20be%20a%20potential%20zoonotic%20pathogen.%20Here%20we%20have%20a%20virus%20in%20bats%2C%20right%20now%20in%20a%20cave%20used%20by%20people%20highly%20exposed%20to%20bat%20faeces.%20And%20this%20virus%20is%20shed%20in%20bat%20faeces%2C%20so%20there%20is%20a%20real%20potential%20for%20emergence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20British-born%20scientist%20has%20repeatedly%20dismissed%20the%20lab%20leak%20theory%20and%20insisted%20the%20coronavirus%20has%20natural%20origins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20report%20comes%20as%C2%A0WHO%20reported%20a%20surge%20in%20coronavirus%20globally%2C%20with%20hospitalisations%20jumping%2042%20percent%20across%2050%20countries.%20Notably%2C%20the%20cases%20are%20starting%20to%20rise%20again%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20JN.1%20Covid%20variant%2C%20which%20appeared%20last%20September%20in%20France.%20As%20per%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Ffuture%2Farticle%2F20240111-covid-19-how-does-its-symptoms-differ-from-flu%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20variant%20accounts%20for%20around%2060%25%20of%20new%20infections%20in%20early%20January%2C%20according%20to%20a%20data%20tracker%20from%20the%20US%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%20(CDC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20has%20classified%20JN.1%20as%20a%20separate%20%26quot%3Bvariant%20of%20interest%26quot%3B%20given%20its%20rapidly%20increasing%20spread%20but%20said%20it%20poses%20a%20%26quot%3Blow%26quot%3B%20global%20public%20health%20risk.%20The%20JN.1%20sub-variant%20of%20the%20coronavirus%20was%20previously%20classified%20as%20a%20variant%20of%20interest%20(VOI)%20as%20part%20of%20the%20BA.2.86%20sub-lineages%2C%20the%20parent%20lineage%20that%20is%20classified%20as%20a%20VOI%2C%20the%20world%20body%20said.%C2%A0However%2C%20WHO%20has%20also%20mentioned%20that%20the%20global%20public%20health%20risk%20posed%20by%20JN.1%20is%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705206960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fapmc7288_bat-generic_625x300_12_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-bat-virus-with-potential-to-infect-humans-discovered-in-thailand-report-4859603%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20new%20virus%20which%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20named%20was%20found%20in%20a%20Thai%20cave%20where%20local%20farmers%20source%20bat%20faeces%20to%20fertilise%20their%20fields.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-bat-virus-with-potential-to-infect-humans-discovered-in-thailand-report-4859603%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-bat-virus-with-potential-to-infect-humans-discovered-in-thailand-report-4859603%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-bat-virus-with-potential-to-infect-humans-discovered-in-thailand-report-4859603%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWorst%20Airline%2C%20Mental%20Torture%26quot%3B%3A%20TV%20Actor%20Slams%20Vistara%20Over%20Misplaced%20Bag%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETelevision%20actor%20Surbhi%20Chandna%2C%20known%20for%20her%20role%20in%20Naagin%205%2C%20has%20accused%20budget%20airline%20Vistara%20of%20%26quot%3Bmental%20harassment%26quot%3B%2C%20alleging%20her%20priority%20luggage%20was%20misplaced%20and%20a%20ground%20staff%20misbehaved%20with%20her%20at%20Mumbai%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVistara%20has%20assured%20the%20actor%20that%20her%20issue%20will%20be%20addressed%20on%20priority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Chandna%2C%20who%20has%20also%20featured%20in%20%3Cem%3ETaarak%20Mehta%20ka%20Ooltah%20Chashmah%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%202012%20serie