2title%22%3A%22Meet%20Denmark's%20Royal%20Power%20Couple%20Who%20Will%20Be%20Crowned%20King%20And%20Queen%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDenmark's%20soon-to-be%20king%20and%20queen%20have%20sought%20to%20balance%20their%20royal%20jobs%20with%20a%20modern%20family%20life%20and%20an%20engagement%20in%20progressive%20causes%2C%20helping%20keep%20the%20monarchy%20relevant%20and%20popular%20in%20the%20Nordic%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrown%20Prince%20Frederik%2C%2055%2C%20will%20take%20the%20throne%20on%20Sunday%2C%20following%20his%20mother%20Queen%20Margrethe%20II's%20surprise%20announcement%20on%20live%20TV%20on%20New%20Year's%20Eve%20that%20she%20would%20abdicate%20in%20favour%20of%20her%20oldest%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20will%20become%20King%20Frederik%20X%20and%20by%20his%20side%20will%20be%20Queen%20Mary%2C%2051%2C%20an%20Australian-born%20former%20marketing%20and%20advertising%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20will%20take%20the%20throne%20at%20a%20time%20of%20massive%20public%20support%20and%20enthusiasm%20for%20the%20monarchy%20in%20Denmark%2C%20recent%20opinion%20polls%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQueen%20Margrethe's%20tactful%20and%20traditional%20manners%20and%20interest%20in%20history%20and%20art%20brought%20her%20strong%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrederik%20and%20Mary%20have%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20used%20their%20fame%20and%20goodwill%20like%20modern%20influencers%20to%20modernize%20the%20monarchy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20their%20fight%20for%20environmental%20issues%2C%20sustainability%2C%20public%20health%20and%20rights%20of%20girls%20and%20women%20globally%20have%20also%20gone%20down%20well%20in%20Denmark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20many%20ways%2C%20they%20are%20a%20modern%20and%20equal%20power%20couple%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jakob%20Steen%20Olsen%2C%20a%20commentator%20on%20the%20Danish%20monarchy.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20say%20they%20are%20more%20activist%20and%20use%20their%20status%20to%20make%20the%20world%20a%20slightly%20better%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20has%20been%20spotted%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Copenhagen%20taking%20their%20kids%20to%20school%20on%20a%20cargo%20bicycle%20-%20a%20popular%20means%20of%20transport%20for%20climate-conscious%20Danes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContrary%20to%20his%20mother%2C%20who%20has%20been%20a%20heavy%20smoker%20throughout%20most%20of%20her%20life%2C%20Frederik%20is%20an%20advocate%20of%20active%20and%20healthy%20lifestyles.%20He%20organises%20a%20hugely%20popular%20running%20event%2C%20Royal%20Run%2C%20each%20year%20where%20he%20and%20his%20family%20join%20thousands%20of%20Danes%20running%20through%20the%20streets%20of%20Copenhagen%20and%20other%20towns%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20their%20way%20of%20modernizing%20the%20monarchy%20and%20keeping%20it%20relevant%20for%20future%20generations%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Olsen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20were%20introduced%20by%20common%20friends%20at%20a%20party%20in%20Sydney%20during%20the%202000%20Olympic%20Games.%20Mary%20later%20recalled%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20she%20did%20not%20know%20he%20was%20a%20Danish%20royal%20the%20first%20time%20they%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20perhaps%20half%20an%20hour%20or%20so%20later%20that%20someone%20came%20up%20to%20me%20and%20said%3A%20Do%20you%20know%20who%20these%20people%20are%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20married%20four%20years%20later%20at%20a%20grand%20ceremony%20in%20Copenhagen.%20They%20have%20four%20children%2C%20Prince%20Christian%2C%2018%2C%20who%20is%20heir%20to%20the%20throne%2C%20Princess%20Isabelle%2C%2016%2C%20and%20twins%20Princess%20Josephine%20and%20Prince%20Vincent%2C%20both%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20youth%2C%20Frederik%20was%20a%20rebellious%20teen%20who%20often%20seemed%20uncomfortable%20in%20his%20role%20as%20heir.%20After%20graduating%20from%20university%2C%20he%20became%20known%20as%20an%20adventurer%20and%20for%20his%20interest%20in%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20a%20Frogman%20in%20the%20Royal%20Danish%20Navy's%20special%20force%2C%20whose%20training%20is%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20toughest%3B%20has%20run%20six%20marathons%3B%20and%20participated%20in%20a%20four-month%2C%202%2C795-km%20(1%2C737%20mile)%20dogsled%20expedition%20in%20northern%20Greenland%2C%20a%20sovereign%20territory%20of%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20Denmark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20he%20took%20the%20stage%20at%20a%20music%20festival%20with%20one%20of%20Denmark's%20most%20popular%20rock%20bands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20talk%20to%20everyone%2C%20and%20you%20believe%20that%20we%20can%20all%20contribute%20and%20learn%20from%20one%20another%2C%26quot%3B%20Mary%20said%20in%20a%20speech%20to%20her%20husband%20on%20his%2050th%20birthday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrincess%20Mary%2C%20who%20was%20born%20Mary%20Elizabeth%20Donaldson%20in%20Hobart%2C%20Tasmania%2C%20is%20possibly%20even%20more%20popular%20than%20her%20husband.%20She%20was%20admired%20for%20mastering%20the%20Danish%20language%20just%20a%20few%20months%20after%20arriving%20in%20Denmark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20wanted%20to%20bring%20%26quot%3Ba%20little%20Aussie%20twist%26quot%3B%20to%20her%20role%20as%20princess.%20She%20has%20worked%20as%20patron%20to%20a%20number%20of%20organizations%20promoting%20issues%20close%20to%20her%20heart%2C%20including%20children's%20and%20women's%20rights%20and%20sustainability%20in%20fashion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20recent%20survey%20done%20after%20the%20queen%20announced%20she%20would%20abdicate%20indicated%20that%2082%25%20of%20Danes%20expect%20Frederik%20to%20do%20well%20or%20very%20well%20in%20his%20new%20role%2C%20while%2086%25%20said%20the%20same%20about%20Mary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705202340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fbgu6gous_denmark-king-queeen_625x300_14_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fall-about-denmarks-royal-power-couple-who-will-become-new-king-queen-4845687%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Denmark's%20soon-to-be%20king%20and%20queen%20have%20sought%20to%20balance%20their%20royal%20jobs%20with%20a%20modern%20family%20life%20and%20an%20engagement%20in%20progressive%20causes%2C%20helping%20keep%20the%20monarchy%20relevant%20and%20popular%20in%20the%20Nordic%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fall-about-denmarks-royal-power-couple-who-will-become-new-king-queen-4845687%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rahul%20Gandhi%20to%20commence%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20from%20Manipur%20today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705202002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-08%2F25%2Ffull%2F1692963170-9784.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fpolitics%2Frahul-gandhi-to-commence-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-from-manipur-today-124011400048_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20state%20government%20had%20given%20the%20Congress%20conditional%20approval%20to%20flag%20off%20the%20yatra%20from%20the%20Palace%20Grounds%20in%20the%20state%20capital%2C%20restricting%20the%20number%20of%20participants%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fpolitics%2Frahul-gandhi-to-commence-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-from-manipur-today-124011400048_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fpolitics%2Frahul-gandhi-to-commence-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-from-m