thy's%20journey%20to%20becoming%20a%20tech%20entrepreneur%20began%20with%20a%20job%20as%20a%20research%20associate%20at%20IIM%20Ahmedabad.%20Later%2C%20he%20worked%20as%20a%20chief%20systems%20programmer%20and%20along%20with%20a%20colleague%2C%20developed%20India's%20first%20BASIC%20interpreter%20for%20TDC%20312%2C%20a%20computer%20manufactured%20in%20the%20late%201960s%20by%20Electronics%20Corporation%20of%20India%20Limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20started%20his%20own%20IT%20venture%2C%20Softronics%2C%20which%20subsequently%20failed%2C%20before%20Infosys%20was%20born.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EFamily%20and%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Murthy's%20views%20of%20involving%20family%20with%20business%20widely%20differ%20from%20Mr%20Premji.%20While%20Rishad%20Premji%20took%20over%20Wipro%20after%20his%20father%20stepped%20down%20in%202019%2C%20Mr%20Murthy%20claims%20his%20son%20Rohan%20would%20%26quot%3Bnever%26quot%3B%20ask%20to%20be%20part%20of%20Infosys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20he's%20even%20stricter%20than%20I%20am%20in%20these%20ideas%3B%20he%20will%20never%20say%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbctv18.com%2Fbusiness%2Fa-mistake-by-wipro-azim-premji-and-the-birth-of-infosys-18776461.html%5C%22%3ECNBC-TV18.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDecades%20ago%2C%20he%20had%20a%20similar%20response%20to%20his%20wife%20Sudha%20Murty's%20wish%20to%20join%20Infosys.%20Mr%20Murthy%20said%20he%20didn't%20support%20her%20becoming%20a%20part%20of%20Infosys%2C%20a%20decision%20he%20recently%20admitted%20he%20later%20came%20to%20regret.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Murthy%20said%20his%20wife%2C%20who%20is%20also%20an%20engineer%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Bmore%20qualified%20than%20all%20seven%20of%20us%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20was%20being%20%26quot%3Bwrongly%20idealistic%26quot%3B%20when%20he%20did%20not%20support%20her%20wish%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Infosys%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705201560