the%20handle%20%40zenpraxis%20took%20to%20the%20platform%20and%20shared%20the%20same.%20He%20shared%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20conversation%20and%20asked%2C%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BIs%20this%20a%20scam%3F%20House%20Hunting%20in%20Delhi.%26quot%3B%20As%20per%20the%20screenshot%2C%20the%20property%20is%20located%20in%20Sarita%20Vihar.%20It%20is%20a%20fully%20furnished%20one%20bedroom-hall-kitchen%20with%20Rs%2015000%20as%20monthly%20rent.%20The%20broker%20asked%20the%20user%20to%20apply%20for%20a%20visiting%20card%20for%20the%20society.%20In%20addition%20to%20a%20Rs%202500%20visiting%20charge%2C%20the%20broker%20informed%20the%20man%20that%20he%20would%20need%20to%20provide%20his%20Aadhar%20card%20number%2C%20WhatsApp%20number%2C%20photograph%2C%20and%20phone%20number%20to%20receive%20the%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-embed-height%3D%5C%22740%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Fdelhi%2Fcomments%2F1937ta1%2Fis_this_a_scam_househunting_in_delhi%2F%5C%22%3EIs%20this%20a%20scam%3F%20Househunting%20in%20Delhi%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cnby%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fuser%2Fzenpraxis%2F%5C%22%3Eu%2Fzenpraxis%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Fdelhi%2F%5C%22%3Edelhi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20visiting%20fee%20is%20Rs%202500.%20If%20you%20like%20the%20flat%2C%20then%20your%20Rs%202500%20will%20be%20deducted%20from%20your%20rent%20amount.%20If%20you%20do%20not%20like%20the%20flat%2C%20your%20Rs%202500%20will%20be%20returned%20to%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20broker%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20being%20shared%2C%20the%20post%20has%20amassed%2096%20per%20cent%20upvotes%20and%20a%20variety%20of%20reactions.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20looking%20for%20a%20place%20to%20stay%20and%20this%20is%20the%20second%20time%20something%20like%20this%20is%20happening.%20I%20declined%20the%20first%20time.%20Also%2C%20give%20pro%20tips%20for%20finding%20a%20place%20(1bhk%2F1rk%2