atted%20like%20a%20batter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandya%20has%20been%20missing%20in%20action%20since%20suffering%20an%20ankle%20injury%20during%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023.%20He%20was%20ruled%20out%20of%20the%20world%20event%20after%20he%20got%20injured%20during%20the%20match%20against%20Bangladesh%20and%20although%20he%20has%20shown%20great%20recovery%2C%20he%20was%20rested%20for%20the%20three-match%20T20I%20series%20against%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20IPL%202024%20auction%2C%20Pandya%20completed%20a%20sensational%20move%20to%20Mumbai%20Indians%20from%20Gujarat%20Titans%20and%20he%20was%20appointed%20the%20captain%20of%20the%20franchise%20for%20the%20upcoming%20season.%20The%20all-rounder%20replaced%20India%20skipper%20Rohit%20who%20had%20led%20Mumbai%20Indians%20in%20IPL%20for%20the%20past%2010%20seasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%2031%20matches%20for%20Gujarat%20Titans%20from%202022%20to%202023%2C%20Pandya%20scored%20833%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2037.86%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20over%20133%2C%20with%20six%20half-centuries%20and%20a%20best%20score%20of%2087%20not%20out.%20He%20also%20had%2011%20wickets%20for%20the%20team%2C%20with%20the%20best%20figures%20of%203%20for%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandya%20also%20played%2092%20matches%20for%20MI%20from%202015-2021%2C%20scoring%201%2C476%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2027.33%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20over%20153%2C%20with%20four%20half-centuries%20and%20best%20score%20of%2091.%20He%20also%20took%2042%20wickets%20for%20the%20team%2C%20with%20the%20best%20bowling%20figures%20of%203%20for%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandya%20has%20won%20five%20IPL%20trophies%20-%20four%20with%20MI%20(2015%2C%202017%2C%202019%2C%202020)%20and%20one%20with%20GT%20(2022).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20ANI%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705199400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fbecc4s3g_hardik-pandya-rohit-sharma-afp_625x300_16_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fhardik-pandya-vs-rohit-sharma-ego-clash-over-mumbai-indians-captaincy-yuvraj-singh-talks-straight-if-they-have-issue-4857196%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hardik%20Pandya%20is%20set%20to%20captain%20five-time%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20champions%20Mumbai%20Indians%20in%20the%20upcoming%20season.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amid%20Housing%20Crisis%2C%20Canada%20Plans%20Cap%20On%20International%20Students%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20growing%20unemployment%20and%20housing%20crisis%20in%20Canada%2C%20Immigration%20Minister%20Marc%20Miller%20on%20Saturday%20said%20in%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20he%20will%20be%20looking%20at%20the%20possibility%20of%20putting%20a%20cap%20on%20the%20number%20of%20international%20students%20living%20in%20the%20country%2C%20CTV%20News%20reported%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20didn't%20specify%20the%20extent%20of%20reduction%20the%20government%20is%20planning%20on%20making%20in%20the%20immigration%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20CTV's%20Question%20Period%20host%20Vassy%20Kapelos%2C%20the%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20conversation%20the%20federal%20government%20will%20need%20to%20have%20with%20provincial%20governments%20%26quot%3Bto%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20provinces%20that%20have%20not%20been%20doing%20their%20jobs%20actually%20rein%20in%20those%20numbers%20on%20a%20pure%20volume%20basis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20volume%20is%20disconcerting%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20said%2C%20with%20reference%20to%20the%20number%20of%20international%20students%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20a%20system%20that%20has%20gotten%20out%20of%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMiller%20said%20he%20will%20be%20looking%20at%20the%20possibility%20of%20setting%20a%20cap%20on%20international%20students%20to%20help%20reduce%20the%20demand%20for%20housing%20in%20both%20the%20first%20and%20second%20quarters%20of%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20why%20his%20government%20is%20only%20considering%20a%20cap%20now%20when%20the%20idea%20was%20floated%20months%20ago%2C%20Miller%20said%20there's%20a%20need%20to%20sort%20out%20numbers%20on%20a%20federal%20level%20before%20looking%20with%20%26quot%3Ba%20little%20more%20granularity%26quot%3B%20at%20what%20individual%20academic%20institutions%20are%20doing%20in%20different%20provinces%2C%20possibly%20profiting%20off%20bringing%20in%20more%20international%20students%2C%20CTV%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20be%20doing%20our%20jobs%20and%20making%20sure%20that%20we%20have%20a%20system%20that%20actually%20makes%20sure%20people%20have%20a%20financial%20capability%20to%20come%20to%20Canada%2C%20that%20we're%20actually%20verifying%20offer%20letters%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BAnd%20now%20it's%20time%20for%20us%20to%20have%20a%20conversation%20about%20volumes%20and%20the%20impact%20that%20is%20having%20in%20certain%20areas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20cap%20on%20international%20students%20would%20not%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bone-size-fits-all%20solution%26quot%3B%20to%20housing%20shortages%20across%20Canada%2C%20Miller%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20number%20of%20international%20students%20coming%20to%20Canada%2C%20far%20outpacing%20the%20number%20of%20homes%20the%20federal%20government%20is%20planning%20to%20help%20build%2C%20Miller%20also%20said%20housing%20is%20only%20part%20of%20the%20calculation%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20immigration%20targets.%20The%20pressing%20need%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20average%20age%20of%20the%20workforce%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20taken%20into%20consideration%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20not%20going%20into%20specifics%2C%20Miller%20said%20a%20cap%20on%20international%20students%20is%20something%20the%20federal%20government%20is%20considering%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20will%20continue%20to%20consider.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20sense%20of%20what%20those%20numbers%20would%20look%20like%2C%20what%20the%20reduction%20of%20those%20numbers%20look%20like%2C%20out%20of%20courtesy%20to%20my%20colleagues%20in%20the%20provinces%2C%20those%20are%20discussions%20that%20we're%20first%20going%20to%20have%20around%20the%20negotiating%20table%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20financial%20needs%20of%20academic%20institutions%20is%20also%20a%20factor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20government%20has%20faced%20criticism%20for%20welcoming%20an%20increasing%20number%20of%20immigrants--both%20permanent%20and%20temporary%20residents--while%20the%20country%20faces%20an%20acute%20housing%20shortage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20CTV%20reported%20citing%20The%20Canadian%20Press%2C%20which%20cited%20the%20internal%20documents%20obtained%20through%20an%20access%20to%20information%20request%2C%20the%20federal%20government%20was%20warned%20by%20public%20servants%20two%20years%20ago%20that%20its%20ambitious%20immigration%20targets%20could%20jeopardise%20housing%20affordability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Liberals%20have%20set%20targets%20aiming%20to%20bring%20in%20485%2C000%20immigrants%20this%20year%2C%20and%20500%2C000%20in%20both%202025%20and%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETemporary%20residents%2C%20largely%20comprising%20international%20students%20and%20migrant%20workers%2C%20are%20another%20part%20of%20the%20equation%2C%20with%20more%20than%20300%2C000%20of%20them%20arriving%20in%20Canada%20in%20just%20the%20third%20quarter%20of%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A17051994000