%20the%20host%20of%20The%20O'Reilly%20Factor%20on%20Fox%20News%3Cp%3EFox%20News%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBill%20O'Reilly%20is%20furious%20that%20two%20of%20his%20books%20were%20removed%20from%20a%20Florida%20school%20district.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EO'Reilly%20has%20been%20supportive%20of%20book%20ban%20laws%20in%20Florida.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20vowed%20to%20find%20out%20who%20put%20his%20books%20up%20for%20review%20and%20%26quot%3Bput%20their%20pictures%20up%20on%20television.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20longtime%20Fox%20News%20host%20Bill%20O'Reilly%20is%20outraged%20after%20Florida's%20book%20ban%20laws%20%E2%80%94%20which%20he%20has%20vehemently%20supported%20%E2%80%94have%20now%20called%20his%20own%20books%20into%20question%20for%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBillOReilly%2Fstatus%2F1745839980885291222%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter%2C%20that%20a%20Florida%20county%20has%20removed%20his%20books%20%26quot%3BKilling%20Jesus%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BKilling%20Reagan%26quot%3B%20from%20it%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPreposterous!%26quot%3B%20O'Reilly%20said%20in%20the%20post.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20investigating%20and%20are%20seeking%20comment%20from%20%40GovRonDeSantis.%C2%A0%20This%20will%20not%20stand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EO'Reilly's%20books%20were%20included%20in%20a%20list%20of%201%2C000%20books%20that%20were%20temporarily%20removed%20in%20Escambia%20County%20pending%20an%20investigation%20of%20their%20material%20under%20state%20law%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Fformer-fox-news-host-blasts-florida-removing-his-books-absurd-1860410%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENewsweek.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConservatives%20in%20Florida%20have%20been%20waging%20a%20campaign%20to%20remove%20ideas%20that%20they%20disagree%20with%20from%20public