r%20OpenAI%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20added%20that%20the%20company%20%26quot%3Baimed%20to%20create%20a%20set%20of%20universal%20principles%20that%20are%20both%20easy%20to%20remember%20and%20apply%2C%20especially%20as%20our%20tools%20are%20now%20globally%20used%20by%20everyday%20users%20who%20can%20now%20also%20build%20GPTs.%26quot%3B%20On%20January%2010%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-gpt-store-apps-details-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EOpenAI%20rolled%20out%20its%20GPT%20Store%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20marketplace%20for%20users%20to%20share%20and%20browse%20customized%20versions%20of%20ChatGPT%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BGPTs.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%20new%20usage%20policy%20now%20includes%20principles%20like%20%26quot%3BDon't%20harm%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20are%20%26quot%3Bbroad%20yet%20easily%20grasped%20and%20relevant%20in%20numerous%20contexts%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20well%20as%20bans%20on%20specific%20use%20cases%20like%20developing%20or%20using%20weapons%2C%20OpenAI's%20spokesperson%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20AI%20experts%20worry%20that%20OpenAI's%20policy%20rewrite%20is%20too%20generalized%2C%20especially%20when%20AI%20technology%20is%20already%20being%20used%20in%20the%20conflict%20in%20Gaza.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-lets-ai-decide-what-it-should-bomb-increasing-the-number-of-targets-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EIsraeli%20military%20said%20it%20used%20AI%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20pinpoint%20targets%20to%20bomb%20inside%20the%20Palestinian%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20language%20that%20is%20in%20the%20policy%20remains%20vague%20and%20raises%20questions%20about%20how%20OpenAI%20intends%20to%20approach%20enforcement%2C%26quot%3B%20Sarah%20Myers%20West%2C%20managing%20director%20of%20the%20AI%20Now%20Institute%20and%20a%20former%20AI%20policy%2