%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20has%20taken%20a%20serious%20note%20of%20the%20highly%20objectionable%20visit%20of%20the%20British%20High%20Commissioner%20in%20Islamabad%2C%20along%20with%20a%20UK%20Foreign%20Office%20official%2C%20to%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir%20on%2010%20January%202024.%20Such%20infringement%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20sovereignty%20and%20territorial%20integrity%20is%20unacceptable%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20statement%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Union%20territories%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20Ladakh%20are%2C%20have%20been%20and%20shall%20always%20remain%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20the%20MEA.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20foreign%20secretary%2C%20Vinay%20Kwatra%2C%20lodged%20the%20protest%20with%20Ellis.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20year%2C%20US%20ambassador%20Donald%20Blome%20had%20visited%20the%20Gilgit%20and%20Hunza%20valleys%20ostensibly%20with%20the%20agenda%20of%20addressing%20climate%20resilience.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20had%20lodged%20a%20protest%20over%20his%20visit%20with%20the%20US%2C%20but%20New%20Delhi%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fus-envoy-to-pakistan-visits-pok-new-delhi-lodges-protest-with-washington%2Farticleshow%2F104199733.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enot%20announced%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20whether%20the%20US%20ambassador%20to%20India%2C%20Eric%20Garcetti%2C%20was%20summoned.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMEA%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20had%20then%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20objections%20regarding%20the%20visit%20and%20the%20meetings%20in%20PoK%20by%20the%20US%20envoy%20and%20we%20have%20conveyed%20the%20same.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMarriott%20had%20framed%20her%20visit%20to%20Mirpur%20as%20a%20diaspora%20outreach%20exercise.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSalaam%20from%20Mirpur%2C%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20UK%20and%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20people-to-people%20ties!%20Seventy%20per%20cent%20of%20British-Pakistani%20roots%20are%20from%20Mirpur%2C%20making%20our%20work%20together%20crucial%20for%20diaspora%20interests.%20Thank%20you%20for%20your%20hospitality!%E2%80%9D%20said%20Marriott%2C%20also%20the%20first%20woman%20British%20high%20commissioner%20to%20Pakistan%2C%20on%20her%20January%2010%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1804839%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20a%20press%20release%20by%20the%20UK%20high%20commission%20in%20Islamabad%20about%20the%20Mirpur%20visit%2C%20the%20British%20diplomat%20was%20%E2%80%9Cdelighted%20to%20gain%20insight%20into%20how%20cross-cultural%20influences%20had%20shaped%20Mirpur%20into%20the%20city%20it%20is%20today%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccompanied%20by%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20department%20at%20the%20UK%E2%80%99s%20Foreign%20Commonwealth%20and%20Development%20Office%2C%20Richard%20Lindsay%2C%20she%20also%20met%20with%20the%20political%20leadership%20of%20PoK%2C%20which%20Pakistan%20terms%20as%20Azad%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarriott%E2%80%99s%20outreach%20exercise%20also%20created%20a%20storm%20among%20Hindutva%20activists%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705162169000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F13143825%2Fs300_Jane_Marriott_photo_June_2023.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fuk-high-commissioners-visit-to-mirpur-in-pok-sparks-controversy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Justifying%20her%20visit%20to%20Mirpur%2C%20an%20area%20claimed%20by%20India%2C%20Marriott%20said%20that%20since%20'70%25%20of%20British%20Pakistani%20roots%20are%20from%20Mirpur'%2C%20it