%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20second%20and%20third%20quartiles.%20Two%20possibilities%20can%20explain%20this%20narrowing%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%2C%20gender-based%20discrimination%20in%20the%20labour%20market%20may%20have%20decreased%20over%20time%2C%20with%20employers%20treating%20men%20and%20women%20similarly.%20Or%20it%20could%20be%20that%20the%20very%20nature%20of%20women%20participating%20in%20the%20labour%20market%20(vis-a-vis%20men)%20has%20changed%2C%20with%20more%20educational%20attainment%20among%20women%20as%20well%20as%20an%20improvement%20in%20the%20kinds%20of%20occupations%20and%20industries%20they%20had%20access%20to%20within%20regular%20salaried%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20over%20this%20period%2C%20a%20large%20change%20has%20occurred%20in%20the%20composition%20of%20the%20female%20workforce.%20Older%2C%20less%20educated%20women%20have%20exited%20while%20younger%2C%20more%20educated%20women%20have%20entered.%20Fewer%20women%20are%20employed%20in%20agriculture%20and%20more%20and%20more%20women%20are%20in%20the%20services%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpandemic-exacerbated-identity-based-discrimination-india-labour-market%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20Pandemic%20Exacerbated%20Identity-Based%20Discrimination%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20Labour%20Market%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20discern%20how%20much%20these%20compositional%20changes%20explain%20the%20changes%20in%20the%20earnings%20gap%20over%20time%2C%20we%20use%20a%20standard%20decomposition%20technique.%20The%20Kitagawa-Oaxaca-Blinder%20decomposition%20considers%20the%20average%20earnings%20difference%20between%20men%20and%20women%20and%20identifies%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20this%20difference%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20%E2%80%9Cexplained%20differences%E2%80%9D%2C%20i.e.%2C%20differences%20in%20observable%20characteristics%20between%20the%20two%20groups%2C%20and%20to%20%E2%80%9Cunexplained%20differences%E2%80%9D%2C%20i.e.%2C%20differences%20in%20unobservable%20characteristics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObservable%20characteristics%20include%20education%2C%20marital%20status%2C%20number%20of%20children%2C%20industry%2C%20and%20occupation%20of%20employment.%20The%20unobservable%20component%20is%20often%20interpreted%20as%20measuring%20discrimination%2C%20but%20it%20can%20also%20include%20the%20effect%20of%20omitted%20characteristics%20for%20which%20data%20is%20not%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETable%202%20shows%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20explained%20and%20unexplained%20components%20over%20time.%20From%201983%20onward%2C%20there%20is%20a%20steady%20decline%20in%20the%20explained%20component.%20This%20reflects%20how%20the%20characteristics%20of%20men%20and%20women%20in%20the%20labour%20market%20have%2C%20over%20time%2C%20become%20similar%20and%2C%20hence%2C%20explain%20less%20and%20less%20of%20the%20gender%20wage%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202021-22%2C%20about%2080%25%20of%20the%20earnings%20gap%20is%20attributable%20to%20this%20unexplained%20component.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F13191854%2FOaxaca.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22876%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F13191854%2FOaxaca.png%20876w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F13191854%2FOaxaca-300x143.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-692853%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22417%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ETable%3A%20CASI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20increase%20is%20more%20dramatic%20in%20the%20case%20of%20the%20rural%20workforce%2C%20where%20more%20than%2090%25%20of%20the%20gender%20wage%20gap%20in%202021-22%20was%20not%20explained%20by%20workers%E2%80%99%20characteristics.%20But%20the%20period%20that%20saw%20a%20rapid%20rise%20in%20the%20female%20salaried%20workforce%20(1999%20to%202017)%20did%20also%20see%20a%20rise%20in%20the%20unexplained%20component%20in%20urban%20India%20as%20well.%20Thus%2C%20the%20finding%20is%20a%20general%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%20size%20of%20the%20gap%20itself%20increased%20substantially%20in%20rural%20India%20but%20the%20increase%20is%20much%20less%20pronounced%20in%20urban%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20larger%20conclusion%20is%20worth%20emphasising.%20The%20same%20period%20that%20saw%20a%20rapid%20rise%20in%20regular%20wage%20work%20among%20women%20also%20saw%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20unexplained%20part%20of%20the%20gender%20wage%20gap%2C%20usually%20attributed%20to%20discrimination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20two%20decades%20have%20seen%20a%20large%20churn%20in%20the%20Indian%20female%20workforce.%20The%20increase%20in%20the%20share%20of%20women%20as%20salaried%20workers%20is%20good%20news.%20However%2C%20this%20increase%20has%20not%20led%20to%20a%20systematic%20reduction%20in%20the%20unexplained%20earnings%20gap.%20Rather%2C%20educational%20convergence%20has%20revealed%20the%20potential%20role%20of%20discrimination%20in%20causing%20the%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20an%20increase%20in%20education%20and%20improved%20access%20to%20non-agricultural%20employment%2C%20women%20continue%20to%20earn%20less%20than%20men.%20But%20once%20again%2C%20it%20is%20encouraging%20that%2C%20as%20one%20moves%20up%20the%20earnings%20ladder%2C%20the%20gap%20reduces%2C%20which%20may%20reflect%20less%20discriminatory%20conditions%20for%20women%20in%20relatively%20more%20formal%20parts%20of%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20policy%20responses%20that%20encourage%20improved%20access%20to%20education%20for%20girls%20and%20enable%20the%20expansion%20of%20formal%20employment%20can%20help%20narrow%20the%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAmit%20Basole%20and%20Rosa%20Abraham%20are%20faculty%20at%20Azim%20Premji%20University.%20The%20analysis%20presented%20here%20was%20assisted%20by%20Hami%20Ameen%2C%20Research%20Associate%20at%20Azim%20Premji%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20originally%20appeared%20in%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fcasi.sas.upenn.edu%2Fiit%5C%22%3EIndia%20in%20Transition%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20a%20publication%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%E2%80%99s%20Center%20for%20the%20Advanced%20Study%20of%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705156416000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F13200128%2FWorkplace.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fdiscrimination-gender-wage-gap-casi-sas%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20same%20period%20that%20saw%20a%20rapid%20rise%20in%20regular%20wage%20work%20among%20women%20also%20saw%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98unexplained%E2%80%99%20part%20of%20the%20gender%20wage%20gap%2C%20which%20is%20usually%20attributed%20to%20discrimination.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fdiscrimination-gender-wage-gap-casi-sas%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20import%20restrictions%20on%20certain%20IT%20products%20like%20desktop%20computers%3A%20DGFT%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705154156000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2019-08%2F30%2Ffull%2F1567185232-8606.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fno-import-restrictions-on-certain-it-products-like-desktop-computers-dgft-124011300454_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20August%202023%2C%20the%20government%20imposed%20restrictions%20on%20certain%20IT%20hardware%20g