20Tara%20felt%20that%20this%20was%20rather%20insufficient%20to%20detain%20a%20person%20under%20terrorism%20charges.%20She%20had%20spoken%20to%20the%20client%E2%80%99s%20wife%20on%20the%20phone%20that%20morning%2C%20and%20quite%20unprofessionally%20expressed%20solidarity%20and%20a%20hope%20that%20the%20matter%20would%20be%20resolved%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETara%20arrived%20very%20early%20to%20court%20in%20order%20to%20find%20parking.%20To%20kill%20time%2C%20she%20drank%20over-sweetened%2C%20lukewarm%20coffee%20in%20the%20lawyers%E2%80%99%20canteen%2C%20and%20rehearsed%20each%20point%20of%20her%20argument%20in%20her%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20event%2C%20the%20matter%20did%20not%20go%20on%20for%20long%20at%20all.%20The%20State%E2%80%99s%20counsel%20got%20up%20and%20addressed%20the%20bench%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20Lords%2C%20the%20matter%20involves%20a%20very%20serious%20conspiracy.%20We%20would%20like%20some%20more%20time%20to%20file%20additional%20documents%20to%20show%20his%20direct%20complicity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20Lords%20they%20had%20six%20weeks%20to%20do%20that!%20It%20has%20been%20six%20weeks%20since%20the%20last%20date%20of%20hearing.%E2%80%9D%20Her%20colleagues%20used%20to%20say%20to%20Tara%20that%20she%20was%20always%20frowning%20in%20court%2C%20so%20she%20had%20learnt%20to%20carefully%20arrange%20her%20features%20in%20a%20half-smile.%20It%20barely%20worked%2C%20and%20in%20this%20moment%20her%20face%20was%20disintegrating%20into%20an%20expression%20of%20panic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20an%20ongoing%20investigation.%20New%20facts%20keep%20coming%20to%20light%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20State%20counsel%20shrugged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20presiding%20judge%20smiled%20kindly%20at%20her%2C%20%E2%80%9CCounsel%2C%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20decide%20without%20hearing%20the%20prosecution.%20We%20will%20give%20them%20a%20short%20concession%20this%20time.%20Two%20weeks!%E2%80%9D%20said%20he%2C%20and%20tossed%20the%20file%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETara%20bowed%2C%20turned%20around%20and%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20courtroom.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20exhausting!%20Nothing%20ever%20gets%20done%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20muttered%2C%20as%20she%20thrust%20her%20own%20brief%20into%20a%20junior%20colleague%E2%80%99s%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMa%E2%80%99am%2C%20write%20another%20essay%20about%20systemic%20delays.%20These%20days%20both%20senior%20judges%20and%20defence%20lawyers%20seem%20to%20be%20able%20to%20put%20their%20points%20across%20only%20in%20public%20speeches%2C%20or%20in%20articles%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20her%20junior%20as%20he%20adjusted%20the%20bulky%20brief%20in%20his%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETara%20smiled%20and%20looked%20for%20her%20phone.%20There%20were%20several%20missed%20calls.%20%E2%80%9CJamal%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20closed%20one%20eye%20and%20puckered%20her%20lips%20in%20concentration%2C%20trying%20to%20remember%20who%20that%20was.%20%E2%80%9COh!%20Gaza%20protest!%E2%80%9D%20She%20dialled%20his%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMa%E2%80%99am%2C%20police%20are%20raiding%20the%20local%20madarsa%2C%20Ma%E2%80%99am.%20They%20have%20rounded%20up%20some%20minor%20boys%20also.%20Can%20you%20please%20help%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20night%20before%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EASI%20Achche%20Lal%E2%80%99s%20mobile%20phone%20rang.%20He%20spoke%20briefly%20into%20it%20and%20then%20looked%20at%20Asghar%20triumphantly%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20police%20have%20found%20the%20stolen%20pateela!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20quietly%20pondered%20what%20he%20had%20been%20told.%20It%20was%20Abrar%20who%20had%20first%20informed%20Constable%20Rana.%20%E2%80%9CToday%20was%20Rahman%20miyan%E2%80%99s%20qul%2C%20sir%20%E2%80%93%20third%20day%20ceremony%3F%20The%20madarsa%20children%20had%20come%20to%20read%20the%20Quran%3B%20so%20later%20in%20the%20evening%20Rahman%20miyan%E2%80%99s%20madam%20told%20me%20to%20take%20them%20some%20food%20from%20the%20ceremony.%20I%20went%20with%20roti-aloo-gosht%20to%20the%20madarsa%2C%20and%20what%20do%20I%20find%20in%20their%20kitchen%3F%20My%20own%20empty%20pateela!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20asked%20them%20what%20they%20had%20done%20with%20the%20qorma%2C%20and%20shamelessly%20they%20admitted%20that%20they%20had%20eaten%20it.%20Imagine!%20After%20all%20that%20Rahman%20Miyan%20had%20done%20for%20them!%20I%20immediately%20brought%20back%20the%20food%20I%E2%80%99d%20taken.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAchche%20Lal%20considered%20all%20the%20possibilities%2C%20then%20walked%20out%20onto%20the%20road%20outside%20Jamal%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20stood%20by%20an%20electricity%20pole%20and%20called%20ACP%20saheb.%20%E2%80%9CSir%2C%20Rana%20has%20given%20me%20a%20full%20report%2C%20sir.%20Raid%20may%20not%20be%20advisable%20at%20this%20time%2C%20given%20the%20sensitivity%20in%20the%20area.%20Then%20we%20will%20need%20reinforcements%2C%20sir.%20I%20am%20actually%20in%20the%20area%3A%20if%20you%20allow%20me%2C%20I%20can%20go%20and%20make%20discreet%20enquiries%20and%20post%20someone%20there%20for%20the%20night.%20Then%20we%20can%20come%2C%20formally%2C%20in%20the%20morning%20hours.%E2%80%9D%20The%20ACP%20who%20was%20still%20nursing%20his%20headache%20agreed%20readily.%20%E2%80%9CJust%20handle%20it%20well%2C%20Achche.%20I%20am%20trusting%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20Achche%20took%20a%20leap%20of%20faith.%20%E2%80%9CAsghar%20bhai%2C%20I%20am%20taking%20Jamal%20with%20me.%20I%20might%20be%20late%2C%20Pushpa.%20Stay%20over%2C%20or%20go%20home%20on%20your%20own%2C%20as%20you%20like.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArre%2C%20but%20why%20are%20you%20taking%20Jamal%3F%20He%20has%20already%20been%20dragged%20into%20the%20investigation.%20He%20might%20get%20into%20more%20trouble%2C%E2%80%9D%20called%20out%20Jamal%E2%80%99s%20mother%20in%20concern%2C%20but%20Jamal%20had%20already%20scampered%20out%20of%20the%20door%20in%20excitement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCall%20Detective%20Habibi%20also!%20Let%20me%20tell%20both%20of%20you%20what%20has%20happened%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Achche%20Lal%20to%20Jamal%20affectionately%20as%20they%20hurried%20down%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJamal%20bhai%2C%20you%20were%20right!%20It%20is%20the%20madarsa%20boys%2C%E2%80%9D%20exclaimed%20Habibi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20yet%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Achche%20Lal%20firmly.%20%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20proper%20tafteesh%20has%20to%20be%20done.%E2%80%9D%20He%20tapped%20on%20the%20wooden%20door%20and%20smiled%20at%20the%20adolescent%20boy%20who%20opened%20it.%20%E2%80%9CIs%20Maulvi%20saheb%20there%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maulvi%20was%20barely%20out%20of%20his%20teens%20himself.%20He%20started%20crying%20at%20the%20sight%20of%20a%20uniformed%20policeman.%20%E2%80%9CSir%2C%20has%20Abrar%20bhai%20gone%20and%20complained%20about%20us%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAbrar%20bhai%20has%20only%20said%20that%20he%20discovered%20the%20stolen%20pateela%20in%20your%20kitchen.%20Is%20that%20true%3F%E2%80%9D%20Jamal%20laid%20a%20hand%20on%20Maulvi%20saheb%E2%80%99s%20shoulder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSalman%20bhai%20brought%20the%20pateela%20to%20feed%20us!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20right%20too!%E2%80%9D%20Habib%20clapped%20his%20thighs%20excitedly%2C%20and%20only%20then%20remembered%20that%20he%20was%20getting%20ahead%20of%20himself%20again.%20He%20looked%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20did%20Salman%20bhai%20bring%20the%20pateela%20to%20feed%20you%3F%E2%80%9D%20Jamal%20persisted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJust%20like%20that.%20He%20likes%20getting%20good%20food%20for%20us.%20Sometimes%20he%20brings%20biryani%2C%20or%20chocolates.%20That%20day%20he%20brought%20qorma.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20didn%E2%80%99t%20ask%20where%20it%20had%20come%20from%3F%20Then%20secondly%20you%20didn%E2%80%99t%20think%20to%20report%20about%20it%20after