Nirmal%2C%20now%20that%20he%20had%20absolved%20himself%20of%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAbsolutely%20not!%20There%20is%20no%20need%20to%20crowd%20the%20holy%20place%20at%20this%20time.%20Think%20global%2C%20act%20local!%20We%20will%20hold%20the%20ceremony%20that%20is%20happening%20in%20Ayodhya%20in%20our%20hearts%2C%20but%20commemorate%20the%20occasion%20locally.%20We%20will%20do%20something%20in%20our%20homes!%20Why%20create%20unnecessary%20inconvenience%20for%20the%20dignitaries%20now%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20disheveled%20and%20sour%20Constable%20Rana%20arrived%20at%20the%20shop%20and%20demanded%20tea.%20%E2%80%9CGive%20me%20something%20to%20eat%2C%20quickly.%20I%20have%20to%20go%20back.%E2%80%9D%20Shambhu%E2%80%99s%20clientele%20regarded%20Constable%20Rana%20with%20surprise.%20%E2%80%9CArre%2C%20Awdhesh%20bhai%3F%20Where%20are%20you%20coming%20from%20early%20in%20the%20morning%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20up%20all%20night%20watching%20that%20blasted%20madarsa.%20Seeing%20his%20mood%2C%20Shambhu%20hurriedly%20brought%20him%20sweetened%2C%20hot%20tea%20in%20a%20small%20glass.%20Constable%20Rana%20took%20a%20sip%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20stolen%20goods%20from%20Rahman%20ji%E2%80%99s%20hotel%20have%20all%20been%20recovered%20at%20the%20madarsa%2C%20as%20expected.%20We%20should%20just%20shut%20them%20down.%20I%20was%20stationed%20there%20all%20night%20making%20sure%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20remove%20the%20stolen%20goods.%E2%80%9D%20He%20chewed%20moodily%20on%20a%20kachauri%20and%20drank%20his%20tea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThen%3F%20Did%20anything%20happen%20during%20the%20night%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Balabhadra%20babu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstable%20Rana%20shook%20his%20head.%20%E2%80%9CNothing.%20At%20one%20time%20I%20felt%20it%20was%20just%20a%20punishment%20posting.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArre%2C%20why%20didn%E2%80%99t%20you%20call%20us%2C%20Awdhesh%20bhai%3F%20We%20would%20have%20given%20you%20company%20through%20the%20night.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstable%20Rana%20got%20up%20and%20stretched.%20%E2%80%9CCome%20now.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBulbhaddar%20chacha%2C%20I%20have%20to%20tell%20you%20something%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shambhu%20after%20everyone%20had%20left.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20night%20Jamal%20ji%20was%20at%20the%20restaurant%20and%20he%20wanted%20gulab%20jamun.%20So%20Rahman%20miyan%20sent%20Arshad%20here%20to%20bring%20it.%20First%2C%20Arshad%20took%20two%20plates%20%E2%80%93%20one%20each%20for%20Jamal%20ji%20and%20Habib%20ji.%20Then%20they%20wanted%20more.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20was%20Jamal%20eating%20so%20much%20gulab%20jamun!%E2%80%9D%20mumbled%20Balabhadra%20babu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThen%20second%20time%20Arshad%20said%20they%20are%20asking%20for%20chashni%20also.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98You%20give%20the%20whole%20pateela.%20I%E2%80%99ll%20bring%20it%20back%20later.%E2%80%99%20Next%20morning%20all%20this%20happened.%20I%20had%20gone%20there%20to%20see%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20and%20I%20saw%20my%20pateela%20lying%20inside%20a%20packet.%20It%20was%20empty%2C%20so%20I%20picked%20it%20up%20and%20brought%20it%20back.%20By%20mistake%2C%20I%20also%20brought%20back%20one%20aluminium%20tiffin%20carrier.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRahman%20miyan%E2%80%99s%20tiffin%20carrier%3F%20You%20brought%20it%20by%20mistake%3F%E2%80%9D%20Balabhadra%20babu%20looked%20unconvinced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20lying%20next%20to%20my%20pateela.%20I%20was%20in%20such%20a%20shock%2C%20I%20picked%20it%20up%20and%20put%20it%20in%20the%20same%20packet%20with%20my%20pateela.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNobody%20saw%20you%20in%20that%20crowd%20of%20people%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%20was%20looking%20at%20poor%20Rahman%20ji%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shambhu%20shrugged.%20%E2%80%9CI%20really%20didn%E2%80%99t%20realise%20what%20I%20was%20doing.%20I%20remembered%20just%20now%20when%20Rana%20sir%20was%20talking%20about%20the%20pateela%20in%20the%20madarsa.%20Bulbhaddar%20chacha%2C%20you%20please%20explain%20to%20the%20police%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20be%20continued%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShahrukh%20Alam%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20write%20a%20murder%20mystery%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time.%20She%20has%20written%20versions%20of%20this%20story%20since%202013%20and%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire%3Cem%3E%C2%A0has%20published%20one%20such%20version%20earlier.%20She%20is%20hopeful%20that%20she%E2%80%99ll%20deliver%20a%20complete%20mystery%20this%20time.%20%F0%9F%A4%9E%F0%9F%8F%BB%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705127402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F13090221%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-13-at-7.18.50-AM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffiction%2Fa-mood-for-murder-episode-7-chashni%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Wire%20WhoDunnIt%3A%20This%20is%20the%20seventh%20part%20of%20a%20serialised%20detective%20story%20by%20Shahrukh%20Alam.%20It%20is%20a%20work%20of%20fiction.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffiction%2Fa-mood-for-murder-episode-7-chashni%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22LIC%20receives%20notification%20for%20tax%20refund%20of%20Rs%2025%2C464%20crore%20for%207%20AYs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705123865000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-08%2F10%2Ffull%2F1691673430-7776.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Flic-gets-notification-for-a-tax-refund-of-rs-25464-crore-124011300119_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20insurer%20noted%20that%20it%20will%20file%20an%20appeal%20with%20the%20before%20Commissioner%20(Appeals)%20against%20all%20the%20tax%20