2%80%9D%20in%20dealing%20with%20Chinese%20troop%20movement%20in%20August%202020%2C%20and%20how%20the%20Agnipath%20tour%20of%20duty%20scheme%20caught%20the%20armed%20forces%20by%20surprise%20and%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fagnipath-scheme-bolt-out-of-the-blue-navy-air-force-former-army-chief-naravane-memoirs%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cbolt%20out%20of%20the%20blue%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20earlier%20slated%20to%20be%20released%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%2C%20Manoj%20Pande%2C%20at%20his%20press%20conference%20this%20week%2C%20betrayed%20the%20unease%20within%20the%20establishment%20about%20Agniveer%2C%20when%20he%20refused%20to%20comment%20on%20his%20predecessor%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20on%20the%20controversial%20four-year%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20him%20as%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20be%20unfair%20for%20me%20to%20say%20anything%20on%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20General%20Pande%20said%2C%20when%20asked%20about%20General%20Naravane%E2%80%99s%20observations%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20here%20on%2C%20we%20need%20to%20move%20forward.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20spoke%20on%20the%20scheme%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20I%20said%2C%20the%20acceptability%2C%20the%20positivity%20and%20integration%20of%20the%20Agniveers%20in%20the%20units%20is%20happening%20well.%20There%20are%20few%20challenges%20in%20terms%20of%20training%2C%20most%20of%20which%20are%20at%20the%20tactical%20level%20which%20entail%20tweaking%20of%20our%20policies%2C%20limited%20training%20period%2C%20harmonising%20firing%20standards%20between%20Agniveers%20and%20regular%20soldiers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Agniveer%20has%20resulted%20in%20a%20debate%20within%20the%20armed%20forces%20and%20was%20not%20something%20that%20the%20former%20Chief%20of%20Defence%20Staff%2C%20Late%20General%20Rawat%2C%20also%20supported.%20There%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livehindustan.com%2Fnational%2Fstory-indian-army-bharti-agniveer-apply-india-preparation-for-major-changes-in-the-agnipath-scheme-8758101.html%5C%22%3Etalk%20of%20the%20armed%20forces%20insisting%20on%2050%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Agniveer%20recruits%20being%20absorbed%20as%20permanent%20last%20year%2C%20but%20analysts%20say%2C%20the%20political%20establishment%20did%20not%20finally%20come%20around%20to%20it%2C%20as%20it%20would%20have%20meant%20a%20significant%20walk%20back%20from%20the%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews%20stories%20based%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fauthor%2Fmanash-pratim-bhuyan%2F%5C%22%3Eexcerpts%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20book%20were%20also%20published%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI%20in%20December%20in%20the%20form%20of%20five%20news%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fagnipath-scheme-bolt-out-of-the-blue-navy-air-force-former-army-chief-naravane-memoirs%5C%22%3EAgnipath%20Scheme%20Was%20%E2%80%98Bolt%20Out%20of%20the%20Blue%E2%80%99%20for%20Navy%20and%20Air%20Force%3A%20Former%20Army%20Chief%20Naravane%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20chapters%20of%20the%20book%20are%20being%20reviewed%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20while%20some%20chapters%20are%20being%20reviewed%20by%20the%20defence%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20excerpts%20published%20by%20PTI%2C%20Naravane%20wrote%20that%20when%20he%20was%20first%20informed%20about%20the%20Tour%20of%20Duty%20scheme%2C%20%E2%80%9Cit%20was%20more%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20a%20short-service%20option%20at%20the%20soldier%20level.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20office%20(PMO)%20was%20considering%20this%20proposal%2C%20but%20with%20a%20much%20wider%20scope%20and%20applicability.%20In%20the%20PMO%20formulation%2C%20not%20only%20should%20the%20complete%20intake%20of%20the%20year%20be%20short-service%20based%2C%20but%20it%20would%20also%20apply%20to%20all%20three%20services%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fagnipath-to-galwan-clash-ex-army-chief-general-naravanes-big-revelations-in-memoirs-yet-to-be-released%5C%22%3E%20writes.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHaving%20become%20a%20tri-service%20matter%2C%20it%20now%20fell%20on%20the%20CDS%2C%20General%20Bipin%20Rawat%2C%20to%20take%20the%20proposal%20forward%2C%20albeit%20with%20the%20Army%20remaining%20the%20lead%20service.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%2C%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20were%20taken%20by%20surprise%20by%20this%20turn%20of%20events%2C%20but%20for%20the%20Navy%20and%20Air%20Force%2C%20it%20came%20like%20a%20bolt%20from%20the%20blue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20learnt%20that%20the%20portions%20relating%20to%20the%20revelations%20about%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%20are%20being%20reviewed%20by%20the%20defence%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20release%20of%20the%20excerpts%20on%20the%20Agniveer%20scheme%2C%20the%20Congress%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1737058915341230091%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1737058915341230091%257Ctwgr%255E84b93666bdab42806d754c6f436f7db89b977168%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fthewire.in%252Fbooks%252Fagnipath-to-galwan-clash-ex-army-chief-general-naravanes-big-revelations-in-memoirs-yet-to-be-released%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20accused%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20government%20of%20%E2%80%9Cbulldozing%E2%80%9D%20the%20scheme.%20The%20statement%20said%20that%20General%20Naravane%E2%80%99s%20memoirs%20%E2%80%9Cconfirmed%20what%20had%20been%20commonly%20believed%20when%20the%20Agnipath%2FAgniveer%20scheme%20was%20bulldozed%20through%20without%20meaningful%20consultations%20with%20those%20who%20were%20being%20directly%20impacted%20by%20such%20a%20disastrous%20policy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20revelations%20in%20the%20upcoming%20book%2C%20according%20to%20the%20excerpts%20published%20by%20PTI%2C%20include%20Naravane%20narrating%20about%20the%20night%20of%20August%2031%2C%202020%2C%20following%20a%20tense%20situation%20arising%20out%20of%20Chinese%20PLA%20moving%20tanks%20and%20troops%20in%20Rechin%20La%20mountain%20pass%20on%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20conveyed%20the%20criticality%20of%20the%20situation%20to%20the%20RM%20(Raksha%20Mantri)%2C%20who%20said%20he%20would%20get%20back%20to%20me%2C%20which%20he%20did%2C%20by%20about%202230%20hours%2C%E2%80%9D%20PTI%20quoted%20him%20from%20the%20memoirs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20said%20that%20he%20had%20spoken%20to%20the%20PM%20and%20that%20it%20was%20purely%20a%20military%20decision.%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Jo%20ucchit%20samjho%20woh%20karo%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Do%20whatever%20you%20deem%20is%20appropriate).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20handed%20a%20hot%20potato.%20With%20this%20carte%20blanche%2C%20the%20onus%20was%20now%20totally%20on%20me.%20I%20took%20a%20deep%20breath%20and%20sat%20silently%20for%20a%20few%20minutes.%20All%20was%20quiet%20save%20for%20the%20ticking%20of%20the%20wall%20clock.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20author%2C%20General%20Naravane%2C%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20final%20release%20date%20for%20the%20book%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20we%20should%20%E2%80%9Ccheck%20with%20publishers%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fem%3EWe%20carefully%20review%20all%20our%20books%20to%20ensure%20quality%20content%20and%20this%20process%20may%20impact%20publishing%20timelines%20based%20on%20the%20necessary%20work%20involved.%20As%20part%20of%20this%20editorial%20process%2C%20we%20are%20scheduled%20to%20publish%20General%20M.M.%20Naravane%E2%80%99s%20book%20in%202024%20and%20we%20are%20working%20towards%20meeting%20that%20timeline%2C%E2%80%9D%20Milee%20Ashwarya%2C%20publisher%2C%20Penguin%20Random%20House%20India%2C%20told%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20an%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Naravane%20retired%20as%20the%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%20on%20April%2030%2C%202022%20and%20has%20since%20completed%20his%20PhD%20in%20defence%20and%20strategic%20studies%20from%20Punjabi%20University%2C%20Patiala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApril%2030%2C%20or%20May%20would%20be%20a%20time%20of%20considerable%20ferment%20in%20the%20country%2C%20when%20the%20news%20cycle%20would%20be%20fully%20consumed%20by%20the%20elections%20expected%20at%20the%20time%2C%20most%20of%20the%20contours%20of%20the%20political%20campaign%20would%20be%20almost%20set%20by%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705123035000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F13104427%2Fimage-1734.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fex-army-chief-gen-naravanes-memoirs-delayed-amazon-cancels-january-orders-not-before-may%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'The%20Wire'%20has%20learnt%20that%20chapters%20of%20the%20book%2C%20containing%20revelations%20such%20as%20how%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%20was%20a%20%E2%80%98bolt%20from%20the%20blue%E2%80%99%2C%20is%20being%20reviewed%20by%20both%20the%20external%20affairs%20and%20the%20defence%20ministry.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fex-army-chief-gen-naravanes-memoirs-delayed-amazon-cancels-january-orders-not-before-may%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22It%E2%80%99s%20Normal%20for%20Your%20Mind%20to%20Wander.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20How%20to%20Maximise%20The%26nbsp%3BBenefits%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12173732%2Fimage-1729.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EHave%20you%20ever%20found%20yourself%20thinking%20about%20loved%20ones%20during%20a%20boring%20meeting%3F%20Or%20going%20over%20the%20plot%20of%20a%20movie%20you%20recently%20watched%20during%20a%20drive%20to%20the%20supermarket%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20cognitive%20phenomenon%20known%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1016%2Fj.actpsy.2011.01.002%5C%22%3Emind%20wandering%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%20Research%20suggests%20it%20can%20account%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0044423%5C%22%3Eup%20to%2050%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20our%20waking%20cognition%20(our%20mental%20processes%20when%20awake)%20in%20both%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1126%2Fscience.1192439%5C%22%3Ewestern%20and%20non-western%20societies%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20can%20help%20make%20this%20time%20productive%20and%20beneficial%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMind%20wandering%20is%20not%20daydreaming%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMind%20wandering%20is%20often%20used%20interchangeably%20with%20daydreaming.%20They%20are%20both%20considered%20types%20of%20inattention%20but%20are%20not%20the%20same%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMind%20wandering%20is%20related%20to%20a%20primary%20task%2C%20such%20as%20reading%20a%20book%2C%20listening%20to%20a%20lecture%2C%20or%20attending%20a%20meeting.%20The%20mind%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.frontiersin.org%2Farticles%2F10.3389%2Ffpsyg.2013.00560%2Ffull%5C%22%3Ewithdraws%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20that%20task%20and%20focuses%20on%20internally%20generated%2C%20unrelated%20thoughts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20daydreaming%20does%20not%20involve%20a%20primary%2C%20active%20task.%20For%20example%2C%20daydreaming%20would%20be%20thinking%20about%20an%20ex-partner%20while%20travelling%20on%20a%20bus%20and%20gazing%20out%20the%20window.%20Or%20lying%20in%20bed%20and%20thinking%20about%20what%20it%20might%20be%20like%20to%20go%20on%20a%20holiday%20overseas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20were%20driving%20the%20bus%20or%20making%20the%20bed%20and%20your%20thoughts%20diverted%20from%20the%20primary%20task%2C%20this%20would%20be%20classed%20as%20mind%20wandering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12174039%2Fimage-1730.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22927%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12174039%2Fimage-1730.png%20927w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12174039%2Fimage-1730-300x198.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-692713%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22612%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDaydreaming%20is%20not%20related%20to%20any%20task%20or%20stimulus.%20Andrea%20Piacquadio%2FPexels%2C%20CC%20BY%204.0%20Deed%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20benefits%20of%20mind%20wandering%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMind%20wandering%20is%20believed%20to%20play%20an%20important%20role%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1177%2F0956797612446024%5C%22%3Egenerating%20new%20ideas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20conclusions%20or%20insights%20(also%20known%20as%20%E2%80%9Caha!%20moments%E2%80%9D).%20This%20is%20because%20it%20can%20give%20your%20mind%20a%20break%20and%20free%20it%20up%20to%20think%20more%20creatively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20type%20of%20creativity%20does%20not%20always%20have%20to%20be%20related%20to%20creative%20pursuits%20(such%20as%20writing%20a%20song%20or%20making%20an%20artwork).%20It%20could%20include%20a%20new%20way%20to%20approach%20a%20university%20or%20school%20assignment%20or%20a%20project%20at%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20benefit%20of%20mind%20wandering%20is%20relief%20from%20boredom%2C%20providing%20the%20opportunity%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1037%2Fa0031569%5C%22%3Ementally%20retreat%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20monotonous%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20someone%20who%20does%20not%20enjoy%20washing%20dishes%20could%20think%20about%20their%20upcoming%20weekend%20plans%20while%20doing%20the%20chore.%20In%20this%20instance%2C%20mind%20wandering%20assists%20in%20%E2%80%9Cpassing%20the%20time%E2%80%9D%20during%20an%20uninteresting%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMind%20wandering%20also%20tends%20to%20be%20future-oriented.%20This%20can%20provide%20an%20opportunity%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1016%2Fj.concog.2011.08.007%5C%22%3Ereflect%20upon%20and%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%20future%20goals%2C%20big%20or%20small.%20For%20example%2C%20what%20steps%20do%20I%20need%20to%20take%20to%20get%20a%20job%20after%20graduation%3F%20Or%2C%20what%20am%20I%20going%20to%20make%20for%20dinner%20tomorrow%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12174751%2Fimage-1731.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22932%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12174751%2Fimage-1731.png%20932w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12174751%2Fimage-1731-300x223.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-692715%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22693%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ELetting%20your%20mind%20wander%20during%20tedious%20task%20can%20be%20a%20way%20of%20%E2%80%98retreating%E2%80%99.%20Cottonbro%20Studio%2F%20Pexels%2C%20CC%20BY%204.0%20Deed%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20risks%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMind%20wandering%20is%20not%20always%20beneficial%2C%20however.%20It%20can%20mean%20you%20miss%20out%20on%20crucial%20information.%20For%20example%2C%20there%20could%20be%20disruptions%20in%20learning%20if%20a%20student%20engages%20in%20mind%20wandering%20during%20a%20lesson%20that%20covers%20exam%20details.%20Or%20an%20important%20building%20block%20for%20learning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20tasks%20also%20require%20a%20lot%20of%20concentration%20in%20order%20to%20be%20safe.%20If%20you%E2%80%99re%20thinking%20about%20a%20recent%20argument%20with%20a%20partner%20while%20driving%2C%20you%20run%20the%20risk%20of%20having%20an%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20being%20said%2C%20it%20can%20be%20more%20difficult%20for%20some%20people%20to%20control%20their%20mind%20wandering.%20For%20example%2C%20mind%20wandering%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1016%2Fj.psychres.2020.112901%5C%22%3Emore%20prevalent%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20people%20with%20ADHD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20can%20do%20you%20to%20maximise%20the%20benefits%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20several%20things%20you%20can%20do%20to%20maximise%20the%20benefits%20of%20mind%20wandering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3Ebe%20aware%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20awareness%20of%20mind%20wandering%20allows%20you%20to%20take%20note%20of%20and%20make%20use%20of%20any%20productive%20thoughts.%20Alternatively%2C%20if%20it%20is%20not%20a%20good%20time%20to%20mind%20wander%20it%20can%20help%20bring%20your%20attention%20back%20to%20the%20task%20at%20hand%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3Econtext%20matters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20try%20to%20keep%20mind%20wandering%20to%20non-demanding%20tasks%20rather%20than%20demanding%20tasks.%20Otherwise%2C%20mind%20wandering%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.3389%2Ffpsyg.2013.00441%5C%22%3Ecould%20be%20unproductive%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20unsafe.%20For%20example%2C%20try%20think%20about%20that%20big%20presentation%20during%20a%20car%20wash%20rather%20than%20when%20driving%20to%20and%20from%20the%20car%20wash%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3Econtent%20matters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20if%20possible%2C%20try%20to%20keep%20the%20content%20positive.%20Research%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.3389%2Ffpsyg.2013.00900%5C%22%3Ehas%20found%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20keeping%20your%20thoughts%20more%20positive%2C%20specific%20and%20concrete%20(and%20less%20about%20%E2%80%9Cyou%E2%80%9D)%2C%20is%20associated%20with%20better%20wellbeing.%20For%20example%2C%20thinking%20about%20tasks%20to%20meet%20upcoming%20work%20deadlines%20could%20be%20more%20productive%20than%20ruminating%20about%20how%20you%20felt%20stressed%20or%20failed%20to%20meet%20past%20deadlines.%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conversation%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcounter.theconversation.com%2Fcontent%2F219490%2Fcount.gif%3Fdistributor%3Drepublish-lightbox-basic%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fprofiles%2Fdr-anchal-garg-1491247%5C%22%3EDr%20Anchal%20Garg%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Psychology%20researcher%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Finstitutions%2Fbond-university-863%5C%22%3EBond%20University%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fprofiles%2Fbruce-watt-1486350%5C%22%3EBruce%20Watt%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Associate%20Professor%20in%20Psychology%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Finstitutions%2Fbond-university-863%5C%22%3EBond%20University%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20republished%20from%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%5C%22%3EThe%20Conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3Eunder%20a%20Creative%20Commons%20license.%20Read%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fits-normal-for-your-mind-to-wander-heres-how-to-maximise-the-benefits-219490%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20article%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem