nt%20of%20saving%20up%20to%2030%20percent%20on%20their%20surgery%20expenses%20and%20postoperative%20care.%20The%20startup%E2%80%99s%20tie-ups%20with%20NBFCs%20and%20fintech%20platforms%20enable%20patients%20to%20get%20zero-interest%20loans%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F299882%2Fmedtech-startup-launches-digital-ai-stethoscope-for-affordable-rural-healthcare-aisteth%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArtificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%20greatly%20helps%20to%20fine-tune%20the%20processing%20with%20the%20auto-updated%20dashboard%20and%20real-time%20updates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20the%20first%20to%20last%20touchpoint%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20model%2C%20Senu%20says%20a%20patient%20can%20select%20the%20city%20and%20the%20procedure%20they%20are%20looking%20for%20on%20the%20Mykare%20Health%20platform.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20pre-medical%20counselling%20team%20will%20then%20call%20the%20patient%20to%20understand%20their%20requirements%20and%20then%20pass%20the%20patient%20details%20to%20the%20medical%20counselling%20team.%20This%20team%20will%20call%20the%20patient%20to%20ease%20them%20of%20any%20worries%20regarding%20the%20surgery.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenu%20came%20across%20a%20report%20that%20suggested%20that%2070%20percent%20of%20patients%20do%20not%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296533%2Fdoctors-innovate-tele-icu-for-critical-care-patients-cloudphysician-health-and-medicine%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eundergo%20surgery%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20of%20the%20fear%20of%20it.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20fears%20are%20because%20of%20several%20things.%20We%20want%20to%20ease%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Senu%20emphasises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20patient%E2%80%99s%20documents%20and%20reports%20are%20in%20place%2C%20a%20consultation%20is%20